title: Chanel Wallet On Chain Caviarskin
description: Chanel Wallet on Chain in grey diamond-quilted caviar skin leather (J6xxxxxx). Featuring gold-tone hardware, a rear exterior pocket, and light-gold CC logo at front flap. The snap button closure opens to a front patch pocket, a zipper pocket and a main compartment with card slots & patched pocket. Approximate dimensions: 19cm(L) x 13cm(H) x 2.5cm(D), and a 62cm chain strap drop. With Entrupy Certificate of Authenticity. (Pre-owned)
